## Logging Standard You Write

Every node must follow this pattern:
```python
import logging
import time
logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)

async def node_name(state: GraphState) -> dict:
    start = time.monotonic()
    logger.info(f"[node_name] starting | session={state.get('session_id', 'unknown')}")
    try:
        # ... work ...
        elapsed = time.monotonic() - start
        logger.info(f"[node_name] complete | elapsed={elapsed:.2f}s")
        return {...}
    except Exception as e:
        logger.error(f"[node_name] failed | error={e}", exc_info=True)
        raise
```

